original: JÖNSSON, Frans O, Fabrikör, Södra Sandby, f S Sandby 22/11 92 av fabr M J o h h. Eft slut skolgång anst fad fma Martin Jönssons Mek Verkst S Sandby (gr 86), inneh dna. Styr.led o huv.m Tornabkns S Sandbykont.
translated: JÖNSSON, Frans O, Manufacturer, Södra Sandby, b. in S Sandby on November 22nd, 1892, son of the factory owner M J and his wife H. After finishing school, employed by the father's company Martin Jönsson's Mechanical Workshop in S Sandby (graduated in 1886), currently owner. Board member and main manager of Tornabkn's S Sandby office.
